CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 10, 1970, pg. 15, reads: "Frogs Dinner - Dancing Party Sparks Holiday Season - Mrs. Fannie Howard of Baltimore, Md. (second from left) was among the out-of-towners at the affair. She is pictured with her hosts Dr. and Mrs. Earl Childs and William Lampkin (right). All Courier Photos by 'Teenie' Harris."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait from left: Mrs. Earl Childs, Fannie Howard, Dr. Earl Childs, and William Lampkin, seated at table in Redwood Motor Hotel for FROGS Dinner - Dance party
